---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="编辑此页" locale="zh" path="/edit/" noindex hasAlternate={false}>
  <div class="container article-wrap">
    <article class="prose">
      <h1>正在跳转到 GitHub…</h1>
      <p>如果没有自动跳转，说明来源链接缺少目标地址。<a href="https://github.com/apache/apisix">打开 APISIX 仓库</a></p>
    </article>
  </div>
  <script is:inline>
    var target = window.location.hash.slice(1);
    if (target.indexOf('https://github.com/apache/') === 0) window.location.replace(target);
  </script>
</Base>
